            },
            "description": "Update the current user's profile preferences.\nID is taken from x-user-id header — no URL param.\nRequired: firstName, lastName. Optional: email, theme ('light' | 'dark' | 'retro').\n\nAllowed roles: admin, player, manager"
          },
          "response": []
